sec.p:
Current parameters were applied as followed:
Channel 1 (Acute pain)—Frequency was 80–150 Hz; Intensity was 0.5–1 mA; Pulse duration was 2–50 μs; Time of treatment of 10 min (38, 39);
Channel 2 (Chronic pain)—Frequency was 1–10 Hz; Intensity was 0.5–1 mA; Pulse duration was 100–400 μs; Time of treatment of 10 min (38, 39).
